    fe-study.Rmd
    sdtm <- new_sdtm(sdtmsyn::sdtm_data_fe) %>%
         add_analyte_mapping('RS2023', 'RS2023')
    nif <- new_nif(sdtm) %>% 
  mutate(PERIOD = case_when(TRTDY> 7 ~ 2, .default = 1)) %>% 
  mutate(FED = case_match(str_sub(ACTARMCD, PERIOD, PERIOD), "B" ~ 1, "A" ~ 0))
